{"tid":2273323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"移民賣樓潮｜中原賣盤按年急增44% 英國房屋經紀：多數客賣樓移民","createTime":"2020-11-05T15:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T16:31:37.000Z","uid":7076,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36fb49d472cfe81aa889245f2b384456a7f27595","tid":2273323,"uid":7076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:51:09.000Z","msg":"受疫情及「港版國安法」影響，香港開始出現賣樓潮，中原地產向外媒透露，該公司收到的賣盤急增44%。<br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》報道，「港版國安法」引發政治緊張局勢升級，很多香港人正打算移民離港，加上疫情引發的失業率上升，同時推動供應上升，中原地產賣盤量按年增加44%至26,000個。利嘉閣地產研究部主管陳海潮解釋，當移民的人很自然會出售原居地的房樓。<br />\n<br />\n由於英國向BNO持有人提供入籍沿途，英國成大批香港人的首選移居地，英匯（Link-UK）董事Eric Yip指，公司在6月至8月期間促的成交，較去年同期增加了3倍有多，其中大部分客戶已沽出售香港樓以助在英國置業。該公司向香港人提供英國房產銷售經紀服務。<br />\n<br />\n不過，儘管市場上的二手供應量不斷增加，但香港樓價依然堅挺，根據中原數據，自今年年初以來二手樓價格下跌不到1%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201105/W3MK5I3JDRGXJLLTJFDEBYH3HI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201105%2FW3MK5I3JDRGXJLLTJFDEBYH3HI%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8lYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=37cd9a2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201105%2FW3MK5I3JDRGXJLLTJFDEBYH3HI%2F&h=359705c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201105/W3MK5I3JDRGXJLLTJFDEBYH3HI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3960684abf19b963d596c67f4dd8a0a65cb133e5","tid":2273323,"uid":248299,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"房屋台:冇人移民/鳩吹/呢次唔同九七<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5218e6c2943f31c02506c0df7563a2e2d7c70a99","tid":2273323,"uid":256127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:54:46.000Z","msg":"唔計"},{"pid":"8b2607ac6a56df6445761ad75f3e1f7eab72317c","tid":2273323,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:57:44.000Z","msg":"賣一間本身租嘅，去英國買一兩間，順便做埋走g"},{"pid":"44d83f3738f26033c6d60cd79e10fbdd40786d76","tid":2273323,"uid":357031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:31:37.000Z","msg":"国安法通過，市民安居樂業"}]}